choices.text: the establishment of the Benin National Research and Innovation Fund (BNRIF) in 2015. The BNRIF is a public fund that supports research and innovation in Benin. It is a public-private partnership that is managed by the Ministry of Higher Education and Research. The BNRIF is a key instrument for the implementation of the National Research and Innovation Strategy (SNRI) and the National Research and Innovation Policy (SNIR).
